WoaS Documentation


Author:
Little Girl


About:
This WoaS mod creates help pages, example pages, images used by the help pages, menu links, and the two files that are embedded in WoaS by default (in case you've deleted them from your wiki). The [[Main Page]], [[WoaS::Bootscript]] page, and [[WoaS::Aliases]] page are included by default as part of the WSIF export process, but none of those has been edited for this package.

